# Frontend Rules

- Fetch data in **Server Components** via `lib/api/*`; use Client Components only for interactivity.
- All API calls through typed client — use types from `@acme/shared`.
- **No business rules in components** — backend owns validation and domain logic.
- Employee directory: virtualize long lists (`@tanstack/react-virtual`).
- Proxy path: `/api/backend/*` → backend `/api/*` for client-side calls.
- Never construct JSX inside try/catch — load data first, then render (see `app/page.tsx`).
